version_description: The song also sounds good with barre E, B and A chords and no capo.

I used easy chords to play the number.
My chords are correct and covers the full song

See carefuly play variation of Esus2, Esus4. This song could be played whit chords made on 1,2 and 3 string. It sounds very good.
